{"tid":84164,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 豉椒牛肉炒河","createTime":"2017-01-17T10:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T14:20:04.000Z","uid":74981,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2fcc5ecb3a40af48688f4262ba4fa9a382cb49c","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n1. 河粉半斤<br />\n2. 牛柳邊5兩 (牛柳邊既肉質比較林同鬆軟, 又有牛味, 又唔貴, 比牛柳好食好多 )<br />\n3. 青椒1個切片<br />\n4. 豆豉1.5湯匙<br />\n5. 蒜頭3瓣剁碎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/b110655db3a8c6b7cdde87089f624f8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fb110655db3a8c6b7cdde87089f624f8f.jpg&h=987293de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醃料:<br />\n生抽1.5湯匙<br />\n米酒半湯匙<br />\n生粉水1.5茶匙<br />\n水1.5茶匙<br />\n油1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n1. 牛肉洗淨, 用以上醃料醃, 油要最後落, 醃15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2. 河粉meet散<br />\n<br />\n3. 燒紅獲, 落油朗獲, 落牛肉炒至7成熟, 撈起牛肉隔油, 洗獲.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/d7162094491a58a548991a2c2bc1abd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fd7162094491a58a548991a2c2bc1abd3.jpg&h=56a2515c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c76d0b91d2381492b3334350e867d239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc76d0b91d2381492b3334350e867d239.jpg&h=49db1de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/0944a6f7973fd23e0b26ba141068abce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F0944a6f7973fd23e0b26ba141068abce.jpg&h=82be5f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/4a137d337203d743cc9da35567cff4c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F4a137d337203d743cc9da35567cff4c5.jpg&h=ff1fa8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/865fae94bc60a9bb6913ff96dbb03305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F865fae94bc60a9bb6913ff96dbb03305.jpg&h=05f37451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 燒紅獲, 落油朗獲,倒起d油, 落河粉大火煎, 煎到微黃炒散再煎, 重覆哩個step數次, 然後上碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/66a4d4d132c1ff3ae8b2b829fb7c02b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F66a4d4d132c1ff3ae8b2b829fb7c02b4.jpg&h=1e4d992a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/aa1e862a338e3ed3816ae609846c3139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Faa1e862a338e3ed3816ae609846c3139.jpg&h=5e442871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/ed03c22b5d856bbe41a8b888ca525125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fed03c22b5d856bbe41a8b888ca525125.jpg&h=3a237c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a081d6e8a6d3e23fae138264c9fae2ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa081d6e8a6d3e23fae138264c9fae2ef.jpg&h=bfa94dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/003864c9c4cafd0bd932a20946ef6c7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F003864c9c4cafd0bd932a20946ef6c7b.jpg&h=851572b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/281678a86d79d57e4ba156b57b2532a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F281678a86d79d57e4ba156b57b2532a5.jpg&h=c60f3dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/de923283885a9e3d41e895b43ec04fe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fde923283885a9e3d41e895b43ec04fe5.jpg&h=91bf2853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 落少油, 中火燒熱, 先落豆豉, 再落青椒略爆香, 最後落蒜蓉炒香.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/efdc6330e398d1ffb757fc9dbdf82d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fefdc6330e398d1ffb757fc9dbdf82d9e.jpg&h=7203d17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/77e4c695999179524d3960b792b577c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F77e4c695999179524d3960b792b577c5.jpg&h=7b272b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 落大半碗水煮滾, 再落3份1茶匙糖, 1茶匙蠔油, 落埋牛肉略煮.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/42f07cf7a983121d1896a183208ee73a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F42f07cf7a983121d1896a183208ee73a.jpg&h=5d5c4e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 用豆粉水埋芡 (1湯匙豆粉加3湯匙水攪勻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c7f3f1cd58d1692cdb99a35991c12471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc7f3f1cd58d1692cdb99a35991c12471.jpg&h=bb0ab675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/298bbd584ac137b4a4e23375d8afe986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F298bbd584ac137b4a4e23375d8afe986.jpg&h=6130acd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 將個汁同配料鋪上河粉度, 完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/92b8bb9bfafd09ecb41f7be2b94f844a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F92b8bb9bfafd09ecb41f7be2b94f844a.jpg&h=c96a70f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c6283b9d53c06c4a428a9ca0181df362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc6283b9d53c06c4a428a9ca0181df362.jpg&h=dda851aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 如果想兜亂, 就會變成咁既樣, 至於想係你老豆老母面前用手兜亂定係廚房自己黎, 各下自行決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c14464e03aaee482876acdfcefe6dfa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc14464e03aaee482876acdfcefe6dfa0.jpg&h=294fa087&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bd0a799ceb3b0ad646206bf083f514470a5efb9","tid":84164,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e60845ac4bfb26cd3ff218fa2ae02ad6d12d3b","tid":84164,"uid":32625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:42:45.000Z","msg":"好餓呀"},{"pid":"921180f970a1e3ce339d92e8536ddf9142b38bb8","tid":84164,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"屌，河粉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c20ddb33fd795c12cd2d319ea530d8da9cd709","tid":84164,"uid":8893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"成日河粉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2842bc15f349c3a9b072ba6cd614c75f9de93b","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc6671abaf1b6360feb930c563930269e246d3f","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好餓呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85def3cdc5ed17284a061c3d689a69cfe129db78","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日河粉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒埋今次, 聽日炒飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c8f416ad67816e61872f8dd13dbb5338d28692","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，河粉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedf5c182dc58c9d7bfdbccc87913dcaffb114ac","tid":84164,"uid":64973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:14:41.000Z","msg":"一定要用手搞？"},{"pid":"a7c4f285c117c45c50447209276a6e384f28c422","tid":84164,"uid":13512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"個鑊字咁寫"},{"pid":"0bc8f643f00dc66cd2f3b1ac0680f7b9e1fc355f","tid":84164,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"好似好好味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6082e0c52e3c66e7372488d42de3ea7d733e110","tid":84164,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"屌你我至愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce286d016c09cf7df7b3251ab39fb1205a8f843","tid":84164,"uid":15818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"河粉好似唔夠焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ad6753eab4d211c74b64091c023da4051afebb","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似好好味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dac0e3ec9eb70ba5d9f0e38d8be35cd55ec671","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>河粉好似唔夠焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n還好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd212999d8a68edc55967a05dd19286184c60800","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個鑊字咁寫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bded6d61649e46436a35e4d3552fc00ed9612d","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要用手搞？</blockquote><br />\n筷子都得既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ca096b84ead2a7f0396ef95b28479f1e681b07","tid":84164,"uid":63970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"可唔可以嚟你屋企黐餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30c2342bf7be6a69bbdb6d28a0fa3fd5fcc7d46","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以嚟你屋企黐餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7e9c9c5ada83dec6433507884bab108f870717","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>材料:<br />\n1. 河粉半斤<br />\n2. 牛柳邊5兩 (牛柳邊既肉質比較林同鬆軟, 又有牛味, 又唔貴, 比牛柳好食好多 )<br />\n3. 青椒1個切片<br />\n4. 豆豉1.5湯匙<br />\n5. 蒜頭3瓣剁碎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/b110655db3a8c6b7cdde87089f624f8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fb110655db3a8c6b7cdde87089f624f8f.jpg&h=987293de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醃料:<br />\n生抽1.5湯匙<br />\n米酒半湯匙<br />\n生粉水1.5茶匙<br />\n水1.5茶匙<br />\n油1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n1. 牛肉洗淨, 用以上醃料醃, 油要最後落, 醃15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2. 河粉meet散<br />\n<br />\n3. 燒紅獲, 落油朗獲, 落牛肉炒至7成熟, 撈起牛肉隔油, 洗獲.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/d7162094491a58a548991a2c2bc1abd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fd7162094491a58a548991a2c2bc1abd3.jpg&h=56a2515c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c76d0b91d2381492b3334350e867d239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc76d0b91d2381492b3334350e867d239.jpg&h=49db1de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/0944a6f7973fd23e0b26ba141068abce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F0944a6f7973fd23e0b26ba141068abce.jpg&h=82be5f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/4a137d337203d743cc9da35567cff4c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F4a137d337203d743cc9da35567cff4c5.jpg&h=ff1fa8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/865fae94bc60a9bb6913ff96dbb03305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F865fae94bc60a9bb6913ff96dbb03305.jpg&h=05f37451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 燒紅獲, 落油朗獲,倒起d油, 落河粉大火煎, 煎到微黃炒散再煎, 重覆哩個step數次, 然後上碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/66a4d4d132c1ff3ae8b2b829fb7c02b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F66a4d4d132c1ff3ae8b2b829fb7c02b4.jpg&h=1e4d992a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/aa1e862a338e3ed3816ae609846c3139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Faa1e862a338e3ed3816ae609846c3139.jpg&h=5e442871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/ed03c22b5d856bbe41a8b888ca525125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fed03c22b5d856bbe41a8b888ca525125.jpg&h=3a237c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a081d6e8a6d3e23fae138264c9fae2ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa081d6e8a6d3e23fae138264c9fae2ef.jpg&h=bfa94dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/003864c9c4cafd0bd932a20946ef6c7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F003864c9c4cafd0bd932a20946ef6c7b.jpg&h=851572b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/281678a86d79d57e4ba156b57b2532a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F281678a86d79d57e4ba156b57b2532a5.jpg&h=c60f3dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/de923283885a9e3d41e895b43ec04fe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fde923283885a9e3d41e895b43ec04fe5.jpg&h=91bf2853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 落少油, 中火燒熱, 先落豆豉, 再落青椒略爆香, 最後落蒜蓉炒香.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/efdc6330e398d1ffb757fc9dbdf82d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fefdc6330e398d1ffb757fc9dbdf82d9e.jpg&h=7203d17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/77e4c695999179524d3960b792b577c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F77e4c695999179524d3960b792b577c5.jpg&h=7b272b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 落大半碗水煮滾, 再落3份1茶匙糖, 1茶匙蠔油, 落埋牛肉略煮.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/42f07cf7a983121d1896a183208ee73a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F42f07cf7a983121d1896a183208ee73a.jpg&h=5d5c4e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 用豆粉水埋芡 (1湯匙豆粉加3湯匙水攪勻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c7f3f1cd58d1692cdb99a35991c12471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc7f3f1cd58d1692cdb99a35991c12471.jpg&h=bb0ab675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/298bbd584ac137b4a4e23375d8afe986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F298bbd584ac137b4a4e23375d8afe986.jpg&h=6130acd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 將個汁同配料鋪上河粉度, 完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/92b8bb9bfafd09ecb41f7be2b94f844a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F92b8bb9bfafd09ecb41f7be2b94f844a.jpg&h=c96a70f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c6283b9d53c06c4a428a9ca0181df362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc6283b9d53c06c4a428a9ca0181df362.jpg&h=dda851aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 如果想兜亂, 就會變成咁既樣, 至於想係你老豆老母面前用手兜亂定係廚房自己黎, 各下自行決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c14464e03aaee482876acdfcefe6dfa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc14464e03aaee482876acdfcefe6dfa0.jpg&h=294fa087&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n各位sorry, 芡汁應該係用1湯昆蠔油, 唔係茶匙, 打錯字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8399e7f76551c7dd89cfacc8878eb6abba8c9a7d","tid":84164,"uid":22689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"今晚無飯食 可唔可以乞個河粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b16d41bb7f449c454a3918feffa67a13757abf1","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚無飯食 可唔可以乞個河粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9c85d5401133de77d9cc4573f2fe34a8df7702","tid":84164,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e688af52351b4068e04aefb30b4548e259d4c8f8","tid":84164,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"有無諗過轉電子爐平底鑊？<br />\n好那油喎！<br />\nAnyway，多謝示範<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ac895333f28bc9426fef00294ca236b8989a18","tid":84164,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n4. 燒紅獲, 落油朗獲,倒起d油, 落河粉大火煎, 煎到微黃炒散再煎, 重覆哩個step數次, 然後上碟<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係黃黃地就兜亂佢 跟住等佢再黃再兜 咁？"},{"pid":"c0388ca256ac5bc7c83f9e2e791db08d510efb05","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4bf71a3e8a35b9f122d8ca3d8d0e7d7b82d843","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無諗過轉電子爐平底鑊？<br />\n好那油喎！<br />\nAnyway，多謝示範<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度油呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b116242e64fdc4826cbecb103f8afd32fd523c6","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問<br />\n4. 燒紅獲, 落油朗獲,倒起d油, 落河粉大火煎, 煎到微黃炒散再煎, 重覆哩個step數次, 然後上碟<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係黃黃地就兜亂佢 跟住等佢再黃再兜 咁？</blockquote><br />\n正確 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e114751f2405d1b6ffa813d4a95911be3f07526","tid":84164,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"河粉好lam鑊喎<br />\n點搞到唔lam鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5be215ab5f02a49ade4463068a8b287dc6f433f","tid":84164,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:52:03.000Z","msg":"幾時整鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3217f367f89aa00bda7b60480f06e135cdf42d","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>河粉好lam鑊喎<br />\n點搞到唔lam鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n獲要燒到好熱，再落油朗獲，然後倒哂d油，再落河粉大火煎同炒，哩個時候就唔會痴。另外，落醬油炒河粉既話，一定要先熄火再落醬油，然後先開大火快炒，咁就唔會痴架啦。獲本身都係一個重要因素，越用得耐，保養得好既獲，越唔易底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742111fc8a77ba8b59e85880935204aa88af6072","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時整鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳皮蒸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6428935a216ed3daea2071158e33372737eba759","tid":84164,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"每次炒完都要影番張唔會痴鑊底嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81228812f39bd316b58d2bab3f052d0da06f4b96","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次炒完都要影番張唔會痴鑊底嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哩個係用汁做ending，所以冇果幅相，不過其實你睇我爆香豆豉幅相，隻獲係岩岩炒完河粉冇洗過，一樣係乾淨既，然後先落油燒熱爆豉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f12ab82f7d2595480063817a150600bbecff5a","tid":84164,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"我嗌豉椒牛河兜亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61311695e99664bae8727721e63e3a81032d50a","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嗌豉椒牛河兜亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e481393123ab01bd6b328ad7eb2171afbf79fc1","tid":84164,"uid":28588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"河粉點先炒唔斷？呀媽炒河炒到變炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250d163682d99aa2b8d220cf0cdf81893199f588","tid":84164,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放假試下整先"},{"pid":"e68f739bbc5f2193a153c757a1349f8f123f47f5","tid":84164,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"點解上左碟先兜亂 會唔會無咁好食<br />\n酒樓茶記知唔知係唔係上左先兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0e90f1a879d285262c71e3c7ad92094541a43c","tid":84164,"uid":30555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:47:32.0