/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161d3fc61cd73b5eafe362e9e0189f9354588282","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T21:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解上左碟先兜亂 會唔會無咁好食<br />\n酒樓茶記知唔知係唔係上左先兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為本來冇唸住兜亂，後上碟食左淡先覺得影番張兜亂相會好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96cd97751091164af0ebe9a653b20b4ccb7f08b","tid":84164,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T21:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒得唔斷係咪要落好多油 巴打煮得好有鑊氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗多油炒，但朗獲就要多d油，朗完倒哂d油先炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}